					View on GitHub
				</a>
			</section>

			<section class="faq">
				<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>Is Tinyburg free?</h3>
					<p>
						Yes! Tinyburg is completely free to use. We're a community project
						built by players who love the game.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>Is this affiliated with NimbleBit?</h3>
					<p>
						No, Tinyburg is an independent fan project. We're not affiliated
						with, endorsed by, or connected to NimbleBit LLC in any way.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>How do trades work?</h3>
					<p>
						Tinyburg helps you find traders and coordinate exchanges. The actual
						trading happens in-game using TinyTower's built-in gifting system.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3>Is my data safe?</h3>
					<p>
						We only collect what's necessary to provide the service. Check our
						<a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about-container {
		padding-top: 5rem;
	}

	.about-card {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		opacity: 0.8;
	}

	section {
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	h2 {
		font-family: "Press Start 2P", cursive;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	p {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	/* Mission Grid */
	.mission-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.mission-item {
		background: rgba(79, 164, 212, 0.1);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 2px solid rgba(79, 164, 212, 0.2);
		text-align: center;
	}

	.mission-icon {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.mission-item h3 {
		font-family: "Press Start 2P", cursive;
		font-size: 0.65rem;
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		line-height: 1.4;
	}

	.mission-item p {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	/* Steps */
	.steps {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.step {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.25rem;
		padding: 1rem;
		background: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1);
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
	}

	.step-number {
		font-family: "Press Start 2P", cursive;
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
		background: var(--gold);
		width: 40px;
		height: 40px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.step-content h3 {
		font-family: "Press Start 2P", cursive;
		font-size: 0.65rem;
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.step-content p {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		margin-bottom: 0;
		opacity: 0.85;
	}

	/* Community Links */
	.community-links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.community-link {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.2s;
		box-shadow: var(--pixel-shadow);
	}

	.community-link:hover {
		transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
		box-shadow: var(--pixel-shadow-hover);
	}

	.community-link.discord {
		background: var(--discord-blurple);
		color: white;
	}

	.community-link.reddit {
		background: #ff4500;
		color: white;
	}

	/* GitHub Link */
	.github-link {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
		background: #24292e;
		color: white;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.2s;
		box-shadow: var(--pixel-shadow);
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}

	.github-link:hover {
		transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
		box-shadow: var(--pixel-shadow-hover);
		background: #1a1e22;
	}

	.github-icon {
		width: 20px;
		height: 20px;
	}

	/* FAQ */
	.faq-item {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
		padding: 1.25rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		border: 2px solid #eee;
	}

	.faq-item h3 {
		font-family: "Press Start 2P", cursive;
		font-size: 0.6rem;
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.faq-item p {
		margin-bottom: 0;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
	}

	.faq-item a {
		color: var(--sky-dark);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.faq-item a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.about-card {
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}

		.back-link {
			top: 1rem;
			left: 1rem;
		}

		.about-header h1 {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.mission-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.step {
			flex-direction: column;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.community-links {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}
</style>
